An extension to Chrome/Chromium to show a preview of your skin in 3D and 2D, and allowing easy swapping between frequently used skins.

Extension page: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/minecraft-skin-preview/abdidfhdgkoepjlnnnbmjahnlhbjgfgp

After installation, visit this page to view your skin etc: https://minecraft.net/profile
